%N A395715 Number of relations on an n-set that are reflexive and transitive, but not symmetric.
%C A395715 Equivalently, a(n) is the number of preorders (quasi-orders) on a labeled n-set that are not equivalence relations.
%F A395715 a(n) = A000798(n) - A000110(n).
%e A395715 For n=2 the a(2)=2 preorders that are not equivalence relations are the two total orders {(1,1),(2,2),(1,2)} and {(1,1),(2,2),(2,1)}.
%Y A395715 Cf. A000798, A000110, A001035, A202534, A005493, A394620.
